  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201305/ca59b3e726274f518deae8f099b9af1a.jpg\" style=\"border-width: 0px; margin-right: 5px; margin-left: 5px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t《英文天天写》是沪江社团一档写作类社刊，其目的在于提升大家的英语写作能力。每期节目主持人都会给出一个话题，积极参加的童鞋还会得到主持人的专业点评哦！想提高英语写作的童鞋千万不要错过哦！<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://st.hujiang.com/mag/135231930/\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 90, 148); text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/d5e293c817a6488d819f0c13a95230e1.jpg\" style=\"border-width: 0px; line-height: 1.8em; margin-right: 5px; margin-left: 5px;\" /></a>去沪江社团订阅本社刊！</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/12/25/b3988dd45480452cdbe7c20fc48b17ff.jpg\" style=\"width: 500px; height: 333px;\" />&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tThis week's topic:&nbsp; Less Happiness (90-110 words)</p>\n<p>\n\tSuggestions:<br />\n\t1) Share your story of happiness<br />\n\t2) Are u happy now? Why or why not?<br />\n\t3) Why people feel less happier nowadays ? 为什么人们觉得没有以前幸福了？<br />\n\t4) Anything you would like to write</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tSense of happiness appears to be rather harder to attain nowadays, especially for those who live in front-tier cities and strive for livings. On the one hand, the young generations, most of whom have received higher education and at least owned a bachelor degree, feel frustrated for their talent when enter into a career with a meager salary. Moreover, it is of unlimited possibility that they cannot afford a house based on their diligent whole-life work. On the other hand, thanks to the one-child-only policy, innumerable aging people will spend their life in Senior Citizen Home. Under such circumstances, it is not demanding to understand why individuals` happiness are absent.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/1710422561158/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p983838/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p983838\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p1016538/\">Quora精选：有些事人们总是太晚才明白</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p1015262/\">双语美文：咖啡厅里的故事</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p1015291/\">10大热播剧集，你都看过吗？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p986483/\">天天练口语，让你想说就说！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p1015174/\">52个字母组成的单词当选年度词 你们认真的?!<